
### GET 'messages' resource without access token
GET http://127.0.0.1:8090/messages

### GET OAuth2 Protected Resource metadata
GET http://127.0.0.1:8090/.well-known/oauth-protected-resource

### GET OAuth2 Authorization Server metadata
GET http://127.0.0.1:9000/.well-known/oauth-authorization-server

### GET OpenID Connect Provider Configuration metadata
GET http://127.0.0.1:9000/.well-known/openid-configuration

### GET Client-A metadata document
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/client-metadata/client-a.json

### GET Client-B metadata document
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/client-metadata/client-b.json
